当然,在onCommand里面要进行多重判断
public boolean onCommand(CommandSender sender, Command command, S ...
这样写不是最好的习惯
用多重的if判断会降低代码可读性以及效率
建议这样写：
JavaPlugin myplugin = this; //或者其他途径来获取你的myplugin对象
myplugin.getCommand("Command").setExecutor(new CommandExecutor()
 {
  public boolean onCommand(CommandSender sender, Command command, String[] argv)
  {
    // TODO Your codes here.
  }
} );
或者是:
CommandExecutor executor = new CommandExecutor() {...};
myplugin.getCommand("command").setExecutor(executor); //这个有java经验的应该都知道

还有一种:
public class MyExecutor implements CommandExecutor {
  public MyExecutor() {}
  
  public boolean onCommand(CommandSender sender, Command cmd, String[] argv)
  {
    //TODO....
  }
}
另一边:
myplugin.getCommand("command").setExecutor(new MyExecutor());

值得注意的是:
PluginCommand command = myplugin.getCommand("command");
这会返回一个PluginCommand类型，这样你可以做出更多的操作
然而Doc中也有提到如果此指令没有在Yaml中注册会返回null
继续在此对象上操作会抛出NullPointerException,祝你好运
